OL,7,FA man who sold chemicals online for
OL,8,F#100 to assist suicides has been
OL,9,Fjailed for 14 years.
OL,11,FMiles Cross, 33, set up a business
OL,12,Fselling the substance via an internet
OL,13,Fdiscussion forum, where he posted a QR
OL,14,Fcode allowing people to order the
OL,15,Fsubstance from him and pay via his
OL,16,Fbank account.
OL,18,FHe received payments of #100 from four
OL,19,Fpeople and sent them the chemical
OL,20,Fthrough the post.
