OL,7,FCross pleaded guilty to four charges
OL,8,Fof intentionally doing an act capable
OL,9,Fof encouraging or assisting the
OL,10,Fsuicide of another by providing a
OL,11,Fchemical compound, and has now been
OL,12,Fjailed for 14 years.
OL,14,FIn one case, Cross was accused of
OL,15,Fproviding chemicals to 26-year-old
OL,16,FShubhreet Singh in August 2024, before
OL,17,Fshe died in Leeds.
