OL,7,F"I would ask anyone who's listening to
OL,8,Fthis who's in a difficult place, or
OL,9,Ffeeling really low, or having suicidal
OL,10,Fthoughts, that accessing specialist
OL,11,Fhelp from people like the Samaritans
OL,12,Fis the way to go, and not to engage
OL,13,Fwith these sort of forums where you
OL,14,Fwill find predators like Cross waiting
OL,15,Fto take advantage of people's
OL,16,Fvulnerability."
