OL,7,FAlison Storey, specialist prosecutor
OL,8,Fwith the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,9,F(CPS) Special Crime Division, said:
OL,10,F"Miles Cross preyed on four people in
OL,11,Fa distressed state and knowingly
OL,12,Fprovided a substance intended to end
OL,13,Ftheir lives.
OL,15,F"His actions were purely for financial
OL,16,Fgain, and he made the process of
OL,17,Fordering the chemical online easy and
OL,18,Faccessible.
